\begin_inset Formula $f,g,h\in\mathcal{F},$
\end_inset

(a) either 
\begin_inset Formula $f\succeq g$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $g\succeq f$
\end_inset

 and 
\end_layout

