\end_inset

, the sets 
\begin_inset Formula $\{\alpha\in[0,1]:\alpha f+(1-\alpha)g\succeq h\}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\{\alpha\in[0,1]:h\succeq\alpha f+(1-\alpha)g\}$
\end_inset

 are closed.
 
