\begin_layout Standard
Weak Monotone Continuity.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $f,g\in\mathcal{F}(\Delta(Z))$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\in\Delta(Z)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\{E_{n}\}_{n\geq1}\in\Sigma$
\end_inset

