\begin_inset Formula $f\succ g$
\end_inset

 implies that there exists 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{0}\geq1$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi E_{n_{0}}f\succ g$
\end_inset

.
 
