begin{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 An event 
\begin_inset Formula $E\in\Sigma$
\end_inset

 is nonnull if there exists 
\begin_inset Formula $f,g,h\in\mathcal{F}(\Delta(Z))$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{E}h\succ g_{E}h$
\end_inset

.
 
