\begin_layout Subsection
Market Behavior and Beliefs.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Here, an equivalence is established between the following definitions.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Unwillingness-to-Trade Revealed Beliefs.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The set of beliefs revealed by unwillingness to trade at 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 is
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pi^{u}(f):=\{p\in\Delta S|f\succeq g\quad\forall g\quad s.t.\quad E_{p}g=E_{p}f\}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
end{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This set gathers all beliefs for which the agent is unwilling to trade assets
 with zero expected net returns.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Arrow-Debreu prices for which the agent endowed with 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 will have zero net demand.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Willingness-to-Trade Revealed Beliefs.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The set of beliefs revealed by willingness to trade at an act 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 is 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pi^{w}(f):=\bigcap\mathcal{P}(f)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To formalize 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{P}(f)$
\end_inset

 is the collection of all compact, convex sets 
\begin_inset Formula $P\subseteq\Delta S$
\end_inset

 such that if 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{p}g>E_{p}f$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $p\in P$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon g+(1-\epsilon)f\succ f$
\end_inset

 for sufficiently small 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
end{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
First result.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
