\end_layout

\end_inset

 If 
\begin_inset Formula $\succeq$
\end_inset

 is a convex preference relation, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi(f)=\pi^{u}(f)=\pi^{w}(f)$
\end_inset

 for every strictly positive act 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

.
 
