\end_layout

\end_inset

[5] The price 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 is monotone if 
\begin_inset Formula $r>\hat{r}$
\end_inset

 implies 
\begin_inset Formula $p(r)/\pi(r)\leq p(\hat{r})/\pi(\hat{r})$
\end_inset

.
